OL,6,FThe ONS hope this will mean it can
OL,7,Fmore accurately estimate of the
OL,8,Fprevalence of domestic abuse, sexual
OL,9,Fassault and stalking against women and
OL,10,Fgirls.
OL,12,FThe government will also use the
OL,13,Ffigures to track its efforts on
OL,14,Ftackling violence against women and
OL,15,Fgirls (VAWG).
