OL,3,COne in eight women victims of domestic
OL,4,Cabuse, stalking or sexual assault
OL,6,FThe figures, released Thursday, show
OL,7,Festimated 5.1 million people aged 16
OL,8,Fand over in England and Wales are
OL,9,Flikely to have experienced one of
OL,10,Fthese crime types. Of those, 3.2
OL,11,Fmillion are women and nearly 2.0
OL,12,Fmillion are men.
OL,14,FThis equates to about one in 12 men
OL,15,Fbeing victims of at least one of the
OL,16,Fcrime types over the same period.
